*.sln
*.sw?

# Test coverage output (vitest --coverage)
coverage/

# Staging e2e build env (regenerated from CI secrets / locally)
.env.e2e-staging

# Generated iOS project — CI runs `npx cap add ios` fresh every build
# and layers scripts/apply-ios-config.sh + scripts/add-widget-target.rb
# on top. Never commit it (see CLAUDE.md "iOS → TestFlight builds").
# ANCHORED to the repo root (leading /): the unanchored `ios/` pattern
# silently swallowed plugins/native-chrome/ios/ — the local Capacitor
# plugin's Swift sources — so the native Liquid Glass bar shipped as an
# EMPTY pod in the first TestFlight build. Plugin iOS sources under
# plugins/**/ios/ MUST be tracked.
/ios/
